      • parseCotEvent

        public void parseCotEvent​(CotEvent event)
        Used to construct the CotMessage object. Called prior to parser.getBundle() which will return the event as a Bundle. Calls to parse and getBundle must be guarded and should be used together in a single thread.
        Parameters:
        event - the CotEvent that represents the message.
